<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Harshly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Harshly,</orth> with a grating sound, roughly: <cit><quote>'twill sound h. in her ears,</quote> <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 4, 7</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>fare so h. o'the trumpet's sound,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 3.6.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. III, 6, 37</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>grating so h. all his days of quiet,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 3</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>